3/ Efficiency for the Supply Side:   In the traditional model, sellers pay for clicks that might not convert. In O4DB, marketing spend is redirected into "Value Bidding."   Sellers compete on their real strengths:  - Can I offer 24-month financing via Mercado Cr√©dito? - Can I guarantee 2-hour delivery? - Can I extend the official warranty? While O4DB is currently a theoretical framework, I would welcome a rigorous technical rebuttal from those leading the industry. 

The goal isn't just to propose an idea, but to find the right partners to stress-test it and evolve the current e-commerce paradigm.
